@Greeny wrote:

You cant get 3bil as the int value in java only goes from -2.1b to +2.1m (aprox) which is why the max money in RS has and always will be 2.1B its also why many merhcants are having trouble… i believe theres a topic on Tip.it…

Im not sure why they havent but as far as im aware Jagex could change it to a long int.

And the command in a piv server for money would be ::pickup 0955
